      <title>拉扎德跟随高盛在沙特设立中东总部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/saudi-arabia-after-goldman-gs-lazard-laz-to-set-up-mideast-hq-in-riyadh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉扎德公司 (Lazard Inc.) 成为最新一家遵守沙特阿拉伯关于外国公司在沙特阿拉伯设立中东基地规定的华尔街公司，几个月前，其竞争对手高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 也获得了类似的许可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/saudi-arabia-after-goldman-gs-lazard-laz-to-set-up-mideast-hq-in-riyadh</guid>
